{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/post/citra-aquaman-lebih-bersinar-di-film-justice-league-yes-no/","result":{"data":{"wordpressPost":{"title":"Citra Aquaman Lebih Bersinar Di Film Justice League? Yes or No?","content":"<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Halo, bro sis! Belum pada bosen dengan tema “Justice League” dong?</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sebelumnya ada <a href=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/mobil-bruce-wayne-di-justice-league-ini-hanya-bisa-dikemudikan-di-video-game-hanya-satu-di-dunia/\">topik tentang mobil kerennya Bruce Wayne</a> di film yang baru premiere tanggal 17 November itu. Ada pula soal Barry Allen a.k.a. <a href=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/ketahuan-ternyata-flash-justice-league-fanboy-grup-k-pop-blackpink/\">The Flash yang ternyata fanboy girlband Korea Blackpink di film Justice League.</a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sebagai fans komik superheroes, saya juga mau mengulik soal film Justice League ini. Saya akan ngomongin bagian yang menurut saya cukup ‘monumental’ dari film Justice League. Yaitu soal penggambaran Aquaman di dalamnya.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_27941\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-27941\" data-attachment-id=\"27941\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/citra-aquaman-lebih-bersinar-di-film-justice-league-yes-no/attachment/isi-5-58/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/isi-5-18.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Poster Aquaman untuk film Justice League. Sumber gambar: bleedingcool.com\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Poster Aquaman untuk film Justice League. Sumber gambar: bleedingcool.com&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/isi-5-18.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/isi-5-18.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-27941\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/isi-5-18.jpg\" alt=\"Poster Aquaman untuk film Justice League. Sumber gambar: bleedingcool.com\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-27941\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Poster Aquaman untuk film Justice League. Sumber gambar: bleedingcool.com</p></div></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Aquaman adalah salah satu tokoh lawas DC Comics. Walau diperdebatkan, namun Aquaman sedikit banyak mungkin <a href=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/dc-comics-vs-marvel-comics-dua-tetangga-yang-jarang-akur/\">terinspirasi dari tokoh Marvel Comics yang bernama Namor the Sub-Mariner</a>. Diciptakan oleh Paul Norris &amp; Mort Weisinger, awalnya Aquaman tidak seperti yang kini terlihat. Dulu (terutama di Golden &amp; Silver Age Comic Book era, alias tahun 1940an hingga 1960an) Aquaman terkesan sebagai karakter yang ‘ramah dan komedik’. Walaupun tercatat sebagai salah satu <em>founder</em> dari “Justice League” versi komik, dulu kesan yang ada dari Aquaman tidak mencerminkan karakter yang <em>‘badass’</em>.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_27953\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-27953\" data-attachment-id=\"27953\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/citra-aquaman-lebih-bersinar-di-film-justice-league-yes-no/attachment/isi-9-30/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/isi-9-11.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Desain Aquaman sebelum era modern. Sumber gambar: interwebtoday.com\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Desain Aquaman sebelum era modern. Sumber gambar: interwebtoday.com&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/isi-9-11.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/isi-9-11.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-27953\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/isi-9-11.jpg\" alt=\"Desain Aquaman sebelum era modern. Sumber gambar: interwebtoday.com\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-27953\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Desain Aquaman sebelum era modern. Sumber gambar: interwebtoday.com</p></div></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kondisi ini diperparah dengan serial kartun “Super Friends” (tayang sejak 1973 hingga 1986 sebagai bagian acara populer televisi Amerika “Saturday Morning Cartoon”).</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_27956\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-27956\" data-attachment-id=\"27956\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/citra-aquaman-lebih-bersinar-di-film-justice-league-yes-no/attachment/isi-10-26/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/isi-10-10.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Serial kartun jadul Super Friends. Sumber gambar: youtube.com\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Serial kartun jadul Super Friends. Sumber gambar: youtube.com&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/isi-10-10.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/isi-10-10.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-27956\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/isi-10-10.jpg\" alt=\"Serial kartun jadul Super Friends. Sumber gambar: youtube.com\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-27956\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Serial kartun jadul Super Friends. Sumber gambar: youtube.com</p></div></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Di serial kartun tersebut, karakteristik Aquaman digambarkan sedikit culun. Walau berstatus “Raja dari Atlantis” tapi desain Aquaman di kartun Super Friends tidak mencerminkan kewibawaan seorang raja (ataupun superhero). Dengan menaiki kuda laut yang bernama Storm, Aquaman adalah salah satu karakter superhero yang paling sering diparodikan di era itu.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_27947\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-27947\" data-attachment-id=\"27947\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/citra-aquaman-lebih-bersinar-di-film-justice-league-yes-no/attachment/isi-7-39/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/isi-7-12.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Raja dari Atlantis dengan kuda lautnya. Keliatan culun hehehe. Sumber gambar: superfriends.wikia.com\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Raja dari Atlantis dengan kuda lautnya. Keliatan culun hehehe. Sumber gambar: superfriends.wikia.com&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/isi-7-12.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/isi-7-12.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-27947\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/isi-7-12.jpg\" alt=\"Raja dari Atlantis dengan kuda lautnya. Keliatan culun hehehe. Sumber gambar: superfriends.wikia.com\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-27947\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Raja dari Atlantis dengan kuda lautnya. Keliatan culun, hehehe. Sumber gambar: superfriends.wikia.com</p></div></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Secara <em>lore/origins</em> di Earth-One (karena DC Universe menganut sistem tata dimensi ‘multiverse’ di mana ada banyak dunia paralel yang mirip, tapi berbeda satu sama lainnya) Golden Age, Aquaman memiliki nama Arthur Curry. Dia merupakan putra dari Tom Curry, seorang penjaga mercusuar dengan makhluk Atlantis bernama Atlanna. Karena memiliki darah Atlantis, Arthur memiliki kekuatan dan kemampuan yang dimiliki Atlantean (bangsa Atlantis). Dia dapat bernafas di dalam air, berenang dengan cepat, mampu berkomunikasi dengan makhluk samudera, menggunakan senjata seperti milik Dewa Poseidon (Trident) serta memiliki kekuatan besar jika dibandingkan dengan manusia / makhluk daratan.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_27929\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-27929\" data-attachment-id=\"27929\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/citra-aquaman-lebih-bersinar-di-film-justice-league-yes-no/attachment/isi-1-81/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/isi-1-24.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Aquaman sebenarnya punya desain keren untuk karakter superhero. Sumber gambar: pinterest.com\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Aquaman sebenarnya punya desain keren untuk karakter superhero. Sumber gambar: pinterest.com&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/isi-1-24.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/isi-1-24.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-27929\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/isi-1-24.jpg\" alt=\"Aquaman sebenarnya punya desain keren untuk karakter superhero. Sumber gambar: pinterest.com\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-27929\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Aquaman sebenarnya punya desain keren untuk karakter superhero. Sumber gambar: pinterest.com</p></div></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Secara umum, Arthur Curry alias Aquaman memiliki semua persyaratan untuk dikategorikan sebagai ‘badass superhero’. Tapi citra paling lemah (jika dibandingkan superheroes lain) serta komedik dari era Silver Age / Super Friends terlanjur melekat di benak orang-orang.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Karena itulah pasca era Silver Age dan Super Friends, DC Comics mulai mati-matian dan serius melakukan <em>re-branding</em> karakter Aquaman di mata publik.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Aquaman mulai digambarkan lebih <em>‘edgy’</em>. Lebih serius dan ‘gelap’. Hal itu untuk menghilangkan citra lama dia yang dianggap tidak lagi sesuai tuntutan zaman, di mana kini superheroes punya <em>yin-yang</em> alias sisi terang dan sisi gelap.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_27950\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-27950\" data-attachment-id=\"27950\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/citra-aquaman-lebih-bersinar-di-film-justice-league-yes-no/attachment/isi-8-35/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/isi-8-12.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Mengubah citra culun menjadi citra badass. Sumber gambar: dccomics.com\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/isi-8-12.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/isi-8-12.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-27950\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/isi-8-12.jpg\" alt=\"Mengubah citra culun menjadi citra badass. Sumber gambar: dccomics.com\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-27950\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Mengubah citra culun menjadi citra badass. Sumber gambar: dccomics.com</p></div></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Hal ini dimulai tahun 1989 dengan komik Aquaman Special #1, di mana DC Comics menulis ulang origins/asal usul Aquaman dengan mengubah beberapa hal dari era lama dan menambahkan elemen modern ke dalamnya.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Diceritakan kalau Aquaman era modern lahir dengan nama Orin, dan merupakan putri dari Ratu Atlantis Atlanna. Karena memiliki rambut blonde (yang merupakan tanda kutukan bagi warga Atlantis) Orin ‘diasingkan ke permukaan’. Dia terdampar ke dunia atas dan ditemukan penjaga mercusuar Arthur Curry, yang memberikan Orin nama seperti dirinya “Arthur Curry”. Kelak Orin kembali ke Atlantis untuk menghadapi takdirnya sebagai raja.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_27944\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-27944\" data-attachment-id=\"27944\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/citra-aquaman-lebih-bersinar-di-film-justice-league-yes-no/attachment/isi-6-54/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/isi-6-17.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Desain modern Aquaman pasca Silver Age. Sumber gambar: comicvine.gamespot.com\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Desain modern Aquaman pasca Silver Age. Sumber gambar: comicvine.gamespot.com&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/isi-6-17.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/isi-6-17.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-27944\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/isi-6-17.jpg\" alt=\"Desain modern Aquaman pasca Silver Age. Sumber gambar: comicvine.gamespot.com\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-27944\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Desain modern Aquaman pasca Silver Age. Sumber gambar: comicvine.gamespot.com</p></div></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Karena komik-komik superhero Amerika sering ditangani dan digambar oleh orang-orang berbeda, maka tak heran kalau kisah buatan mereka bisa berbeda-beda, tergantung siapa yang menulis naskah dan menggambarnya. Hal ini juga terjadi di Aquaman.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_27932\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-27932\" data-attachment-id=\"27932\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/citra-aquaman-lebih-bersinar-di-film-justice-league-yes-no/attachment/isi-2-75/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/isi-2-24.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Design Aquaman cukup variatif. Sumber gambar: boybluesdcu.devianart.com\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Design Aquaman cukup variatif. Sumber gambar: boybluesdcu.devianart.com&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/isi-2-24.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/isi-2-24.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-27932\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/isi-2-24.jpg\" alt=\"Design Aquaman cukup variatif. Sumber gambar: boybluesdcu.devianart.com\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-27932\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Design Aquaman cukup variatif. Sumber gambar: boybluesdcu.devianart.com</p></div></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Di film Justice League, kisah Aquaman tidak dimulai dari salah satu <em>origins</em> yang ada. Ini mungkin merupakan cara cepat dari DC Comics membangun <em>hype</em> untuk film “Aquaman” solo yang sedang memasuki tahap pasca produksi dan akan dirilis tahun 2018 nanti.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_27935\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-27935\" data-attachment-id=\"27935\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/citra-aquaman-lebih-bersinar-di-film-justice-league-yes-no/attachment/isi-3-73/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/isi-3-24.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Jason Momoa (Aquaman), James Wan (Sutradara) &#038; Amber Heard (Mera, istri Aquaman) di lokasi syuting film Aquaman. Sumber gambar: comicbook.com\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Jason Momoa (Aquaman), James Wan (Sutradara) &#038; Amber Heard (Mera, istri Aquaman) di lokasi syuting film Aquaman. Sumber gambar: comicbook.com&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/isi-3-24.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/isi-3-24.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-27935\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/isi-3-24.jpg\" alt=\"Jason Momoa (Aquaman), James Wan (Sutradara) &amp; Amber Heard (Mera, istri Aquaman) di lokasi syuting film Aquaman. Sumber gambar: comicbook.com\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-27935\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Jason Momoa (Aquaman), James Wan (Sutradara) &amp; Amber Heard (Mera, istri Aquaman) di lokasi syuting film Aquaman. Sumber gambar: comicbook.com</p></div></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Pemilihan Jason Momoa sebagai Arthur Curry/Aquaman juga terbilang mengejutkan awalnya, tapi sambutan meriah fans melegakan para produser di Warner Bros. Terkenal sebagai <a href=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/inilah-alasan-mengapa-serial-tv-game-thrones-sangat-populer-penasaran/\">karakter <em>macho</em> Khal Drogo di serial tv fenomenal Game of Thrones </a> , Jason Momoa sukses memberikan kesan pertama pada Aquaman di layar lebar sebagai karakter dengan tampilan garang, <em>ruthless</em>, tapi tetap tampan dan menarik.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_27938\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-27938\" data-attachment-id=\"27938\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/citra-aquaman-lebih-bersinar-di-film-justice-league-yes-no/attachment/isi-4-72/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/isi-4-24.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Desain Aquaman di film Justice League tampil macho. Sumber gambar: business2community.com\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Desain Aquaman di film Justice League tampil macho. Sumber gambar: business2community.com&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/isi-4-24.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/isi-4-24.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-27938\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/isi-4-24.jpg\" alt=\"Desain Aquaman di film Justice League tampil macho. Sumber gambar: business2community.com\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-27938\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Desain Aquaman di film Justice League tampil macho. Sumber gambar: business2community.com</p></div></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kombinasi tersebut dibutuhkan untuk menampilkan citra baru Aquaman sebagai jagoan <em>badass</em> yang keren dan enggak culun seperti era lama. Melihat aksinya di film Justice League, para fans film superheroes DC Comics tentu makin tidak sabar menantikan film “Aquaman” tahun 2018 nanti.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Menurut bro sis, Aquaman lebih cocok culun seperti di kartun Super Friends atau gahar kayak di film Justice League? Pendapat bro sis bisa ditulis di bagian komen ya.</p>\n"}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"id":"8c4ebf71-2bb9-58dd-a2cf-ff0ce5231a58"}}}